01:07:52.790 --> 01:07:56.660
to actually get at more
detailed interventions

01:07:56.660 --> 01:07:58.140
that I could perhaps map out.

01:07:58.140 --> 01:08:01.100
So if you designed a
target trial to say,

01:08:01.100 --> 01:08:03.140
